{"tid":273654,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[警訊] [少圖]  22日苦難印度神遊","createTime":"2017-06-06T17:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T13:51:14.000Z","uid":103088,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"737af7a9a8e94edcedaa034546a761273c80553c","tid":273654,"uid":103088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"同左兩個朋友一齊去左印度<br />\n<br />\n原本日日都已經曬到死 無精神動力去寫遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知偏偏今日原定坐2A 既火車(有冷氣)full左<br />\n<br />\n所有ac class都無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n局住要坐sleeper <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s0rw7n1h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs0rw7n1h&h=befc7cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅環境 熱到痴線天氣<br />\n<br />\n坐成11個鐘真係人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咁多時間 又訓唔到<br />\n<br />\n係時候上黎開post <br />\n<br />\n整返個印度警訊+遊記<br />\n<br />\n方便各巴絲打去印度經歷苦難<br />\n<br />\n都唔會比人呃太多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c68915b5b8a662d6049ce420ad7b3b9a92aa18d","tid":273654,"uid":67448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"好想去印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692128e5d36ab54433e022aeee9f1dcd5aba0571","tid":273654,"uid":103088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"序<br />\n<br />\n原本我自己都係一個好鐘意去旅行去冒險嘅人<br />\n<br />\n適逢今年畢業<br />\n<br />\n就決定同兩個朋友一齊去冒險 玩個長旅行<br />\n<br />\n由於朋友A係社畜嘅關係<br />\n<br />\n12號朋友A就會返香港<br />\n<br />\n而我同朋友B就會飛去孟買繼續鬼國之旅<br />\n<br />\n原本一開始係決定左去埃及旅行<br />\n<br />\n但朋友A一成功請假<br />\n<br />\nISIS就炸左埃及<br />\n<br />\n當我地再決定去北韓<br />\n<br />\n金仔又開始多動作<br />\n<br />\n最尾我地決定去唔成埃及 <br />\n<br />\n都要去另一個四大文明古國<br />\n<br />\n所以就算知印度成為強姦鬼國 <br />\n<br />\n都無有怕照去！<br />\n<br />\n雖然有d 景點真係好靚<br />\n<br />\n但暫時黎講 印度都係一個苦難之旅<br />\n<br />\n網上講過既呃錢方法 騙子<br />\n<br />\n好多我地都成功爭取去經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺我地好似取西經咁 <br />\n<br />\n每日都總會遇到一劫<br />\n<br />\n周圍總會有d 蚌精蟹精想dap我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af931980125d94539e7869e811a1015e15517041","tid":273654,"uid":104356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2073f8da40b43234eb430b4554b92597d2036cd9","tid":273654,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:55:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲一兩年想行陸路去印度"},{"pid":"eddeb28543d64018742dbe9c14dd1a40254b8728","tid":273654,"uid":73000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39e077bace04aec3f12df99d144a479fb8eacb9","tid":273654,"uid":105884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:20:36.000Z","msg":"留名 求經歷 想知如果無人一齊去 一個人去你夠唔夠疆去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b09305a4fb49127a844c92a1325bd7c0824af6","tid":273654,"uid":66423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80282e5fc5cf1393aee59e036f0ff33c63ee99c","tid":273654,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"留名, 準備一個去南印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7740e8703ca87a4b2b99b4a9fa852a1d3344b9f","tid":273654,"uid":103088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"第一日<br />\n<br />\n所謂萬事起頭難 <br />\n<br />\n所以第一日都算係暫時最苦難嘅其一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一開始搭飛機<br />\n<br />\n就已經好容易感受到強國人果種無禮貌<br />\n<br />\n當D空少推住部餐車<br />\n<br />\nD強國人係直接伸隻手入去拎零食<br />\n<br />\n重要成個大袋咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連個印度空少見到都側曬頭<br />\n<br />\n真係樣衰到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落機就已經感受到印度果種hea同懶散<br />\n<br />\ne-visa有好多個counter <br />\n<br />\n但其實上得一個counter係有人<br />\n<br />\n埋到去 佢已經好hea咁同你做入境<br />\n<br />\n做做下又會唔出聲咁走左去<br />\n<br />\n返到黎又會去左其他counter度執下野<br />\n<br />\n最尾先返黎慢慢同你做埋個入境<br />\n<br />\n完全唔知發生緊咩事<br />\n<br />\n效率又極慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8p4bezc0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8p4bezc0&h=2c9ba3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機場既廁所 又幾過癮<br />\n<br />\n之後我地就搭機場快綫由機場入新德里市中心<br />\n<br />\n快線60Rs一程 對印度人黎都算貴<br />\n<br />\n所以都無咩人搭亦都叫好乾淨企理<br />\n<br />\n同平時大家想像 D人堆到上車頂係好唔同<br />\n<br />\n成程車都好舒服 好輕鬆咁到左新德里<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h64wly7t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh64wly7t&h=3933a766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vmw8hoxk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvmw8hoxk&h=60fc9753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度車飛<br />\n<br />\n但由一踏出新德里車站<br />\n<br />\n惡夢 苦難先正式開始&hellip;&hellip;."},{"pid":"72fea73e3510a2e54678f3798aa04de76fe4a025","tid":273654,"uid":73111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會出到一半唔見左人"},{"pid":"36546ba0765ba21d0c86975526aaa9505ffa3bcc","tid":273654,"uid":97431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"14bd98d4fb3072f0f5bbe2eaf45cb2ef61ee8fdb","tid":273654,"uid":103088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 求經歷 想知如果無人一齊去 一個人去你夠唔夠疆去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係hostel 都見到唔少一個人黎印度玩<br />\n感覺上都ok 安全<br />\n一個人重可以借D二 揾埋d鬼妹一齊去玩<br />\n你都咪話唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果無鬼妹相伴<br />\n個人覺得一人可能會有d苦悶<br />\n因為d印度交通 印度佬都好煩<br />\n有個fd分擔下 一齊數苦會好D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005d7c586eb0d89f88382900b1c7725a6313fbaf","tid":273654,"uid":74629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:22:51.000Z","msg":"留明<br />\n我都想趁後生去印度見識下"},{"pid":"7f72b2857bf9e4856fe274958f6044c4a876599a","tid":273654,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24be1b33760b3d9382352fba78b3651ab89a8806","tid":273654,"uid":77363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"61759b3e504e165bb66be7b297cdceed635cda20","tid":273654,"uid":43621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0875bec2ff7c00b5793d613a407c2f22e86d3dce","tid":273654,"uid":65142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b1bb584c249e2310b621e845e00afaa198b47aef","tid":273654,"uid":77057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"快線係最好坐之後就地鐵 但都係鐘意坐火車 冇門又唔會停定要跑住上落車 好撚正"},{"pid":"1f93be9b4ec07dd4626b1ec6776b145af90c15bc","tid":273654,"uid":77057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名 求經歷 想知如果無人一齊去 一個人去你夠唔夠疆去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係hostel 都見到唔少一個人黎印度玩<br />\n感覺上都ok 安全<br />\n一個人重可以借D二 揾埋d鬼妹一齊去玩<br />\n你都咪話唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果無鬼妹相伴<br />\n個人覺得一人可能會有d苦悶<br />\n因為d印度交通 印度佬都好煩<br />\n有個fd分擔下 一齊數苦會好D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀 好撚多印度人都好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d798a2980b2ae213921e61110665500d4de98f37","tid":273654,"uid":103088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快線係最好坐之後就地鐵 但都係鐘意坐火車 冇門又唔會停定要跑住上落車 好撚正</blockquote><br />\n因為我地hostel係新德里站附近<br />\n所以坐完機鐵就出<br />\n之後去其他城市 景點就地鐵 火車 巴士都有試過"},{"pid":"0c34109ba1eb0199ac2dcd7522e41df7d823ef20","tid":273654,"uid":103088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名 求經歷 想知如果無人一齊去 一個人去你夠唔夠疆去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係hostel 都見到唔少一個人黎印度玩<br />\n感覺上都ok 安全<br />\n一個人重可以借D二 揾埋d鬼妹一齊去玩<br />\n你都咪話唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果無鬼妹相伴<br />\n個人覺得一人可能會有d苦悶<br />\n因為d印度交通 印度佬都好煩<br />\n有個fd分擔下 一齊數苦會好D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀 好撚多印度人都好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錢來往就好友善 好正既<br />\n但一有錢 就好容易出事<br />\n普通係街行都已經勁多的士taktak佬煩住"},{"pid":"bc3782811086455ffe0f711728e039d2b83fb9bf","tid":273654,"uid":77057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>快線係最好坐之後就地鐵 但都係鐘意坐火車 冇門又唔會停定要跑住上落車 好撚正</blockquote><br />\n因為我地hostel係新德里站附近<br />\n所以坐完機鐵就出<br />\n之後去其他城市 景點就地鐵 火車 巴士都有試過</blockquote><br />\n坐埋禿禿車 有大麻食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fb0d96d7a819f0207465da1218de57c4d08a2f","tid":273654,"uid":46678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"巴打小心菊花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf17c54fa757580f94a57fe2d959cbcc8f49818","tid":273654,"uid":103088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>快線係最好坐之後就地鐵 但都係鐘意坐火車 冇門又唔會停定要跑住上落車 好撚正</blockquote><br />\n因為我地hostel係新德里站附近<br />\n所以坐完機鐵就出<br />\n之後去其他城市 景點就地鐵 火車 巴士都有試過</blockquote><br />\n坐埋禿禿車 有大麻食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntuktuk就緊係有坐<br />\n大麻就唔講啦 不了<br />\n<br />\n因為我諗住半警訊半遊記咁打<br />\n可能都係主要講下特別野有趣野 <br />\n講下印度會點呃人錢咁<br />\n所以可能唔會好詳細講景點 坐d咩咁"}]}